title: Iran Embassy pays tribute to Fatima Jinnah on birth anniversary
content:
ISLAMABAD, July 31 (APP):Iran Embassy on Wednesday paid tribute to Madr-e-Millat, Mohtarama Fatima Jinnah, on her 131st birth anniversary.
The embassy, in a statement, termed her character fully inspiring as a women and leader.
